myapp # main folder shiny app
|--- data # subfolder for data
|--- www  # public access subfolder 
   |--- images # subfolder for images
      |--- image1.jpg
      |--- image2.png
      |--- favicon.ico
   |--- css # subfolder for CSS files
      |--- style.css # CSS files 
   |--- js # subfolder for JavaScript files
      |--- file.js # JavaScript files 
   |--- <others> # subfolder for others
|--- R # folder for R script, automatically run alphabetically (default) 
   |--- scripts.R 
|--- myapp.Rproj # RStudio project file
|--- app.R # main shiny app R file
|--- global.R # global R file if needed, source("global.R")